data.description: As you walk through the front door and through the foyer you will walk into a  large open area consisting of a huge family room that features wood floors, a fireplace and built ins. Many windows throughout the home allow for natural sunlight. The kitchen offers a split-level breakfast bar with lots of cabinet space. The Master bedroom and bathroom are off of the family room that features his/her vanities, separate shower, jetted tub, huge walk in closets. The 3 bedrooms include great closet space and share a hall bath. Enjoy the large back extended patio and a fantastic backyard with a view of the subdivision pond. This home also sits on a side/dead-end street. *Roof is less than 1 month old!  Schedule your private showing today!  Sound system, shed, and fridge to remain.
